# System Architecture

This repository contains:
- a minimal example L9 engine in `engine/`
- a deterministic-first governance control plane in `tools/review/`

## Boundaries
- `engine/` is runtime domain logic only.
- `tools/review/` is governance tooling only.
- `engine/handlers.py` is the only runtime chassis bridge.
- `tools/review/` must never be imported by runtime modules.
- No FastAPI, Starlette, uvicorn, or route definitions belong in `engine/`.

## Execution path
ChangeProposal -> classifier/analyzers -> aggregate -> GovernanceDecision
